Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,THE TERRIFYING CURSE FIELD
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye little Princess.\NGo act tough on your way to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it for someone who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you even touch Leona, you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai jumped off and charged in alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we land let's charge in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Baduck, stay here and keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the Balloon Ship ready to launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll regret it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocky little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to hurt me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast! Could it be...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to avenge Hyunckel, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In your dreams, you snotty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Mahiado!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze! Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Fire Earth Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was right!\NNo wonder he beat Crocodine and Hyunckel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In his battles\Nwith the other Legion Commanders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the little brat's combat skills\Nhave leveled up unbelievably!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This might be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}time for my trump card!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh wow! Oh wow, Dai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've learned to properly use magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a little relieved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Maam, Miss Amy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Help everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Amy, help Marin first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard did all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like\Nwe've got the upper hand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. You're a much bigger fish\Nthan that little princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,H-His arm grew back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your head is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Blizzblaze Shrapnel Detonation!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! It hurts bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one in pain, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying and help everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take more than that to beat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That little thing was both an attack\Nand a signal to my servants...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin an infernal battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that blast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You need my help down there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Flame Spire is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Ice Spire is complete, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, let's begin\Nour entertaining showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The shaking stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?! What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blizzblaze Curse Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blizzblaze... Curse Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate tactic that's made\Nmy Blizzblaze Legion unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all out of options now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can do now is scramble around\Nuntil you're all slaughtered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real! You can't slaughter us\Nwith just a little shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Cry and beg all you like,\Nbut it's over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My spell... I can't cast Gira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,C-could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nullified our magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you haven't gotten the rules yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like... It's like\Nmy strength is gone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!\NHow did Flazzard suddenly get so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. I haven't gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all gotten weaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That Dark Flame Spire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that Dark Ice Spire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,act on the core inside my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and encase this entire area\Nwith a powerful field!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Within this field,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody but me is weakened\Nand can't use spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, right now, this kid\Nis weaker than a normal human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you finally get the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's cheating, Flazzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you fight fair and square?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me the sermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning is what I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaughter time! Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good!\NMy Magic Bullet Gun doesn't work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}AVAN STRASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}FIVE FINGER FLARES{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy, is your sister alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive. But I can't cast Hoimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, my sister and Apollo\Nand everyone will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, we have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What are you talking about, Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to save the survivors and\Ntake the Balloon Ship outside the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our only option!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to lose to that cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you survive, you haven't lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate, we'll all be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to be frozen solid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or turned into a cinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We can't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, stop being stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not running!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just put up the field.\NI can't have you running now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it so you don't even think\Nabout running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There. You like that?\NThe Princess of Papnica in ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, though.\NShe's still alive in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I used Legendary Forbidden Magic\Nto freeze her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No blow can shatter it\Nand no spell can melt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me, and the ice melts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you still want to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't abandon your little princess\Nand flee like mice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard being a Hero, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Darn it!\N-Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help Miss Amy and get everyone\Nto the Balloon Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We can't abandon the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll just be slaughtered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get out\Nand wait for an opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us, Baduck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got\Nthat much strength in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In this field, my enemies' strength\Nbecomes one fifth what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, normally, that blow\Nwould be five times stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in here, it'll never amount\Nto a mortal wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, we have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!\NYou saw what he did to Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you're alive,\Nhe won't kill the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We should escape and formulate a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fighting to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Come on, big Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell! You're going nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why that little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck was that explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A bullet from my Magic Bullet Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw a bullet with a Gira spell in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard's Merazoma set it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's smart thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Amy, where shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,North it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a rocky coast\Nwhere we should be able to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dancing Flame Army of the Dark Flame Spire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock them out of the sky!\NDon't let them off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there, little Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He ain't the sort of Hero\Nto abandon you, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I feel like running\Nthe moment it gets dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have done something\Nto save the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't done what you did,\Nwe'd have been wiped out by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursuers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us out of here, old timer!\NAt full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadain!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, we're out of the field,\Nso we can use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there's too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to fall into the whirlpool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our altitude keeps dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're crashing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us to shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the weights!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A light came from there and saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? The fools from the balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're all okay\Nthen feel free to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! You have to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything to do with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Matoriv!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and his friends were saved\Nfrom Flazzard's pursuers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by Matoriv, a Mage\Nliving as a hermit in a cave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They work on a plan to break\Nthe Forbidden Magic and save Leona.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Hadlar and his Dark Army\Nbegin suspicious preparations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Grand Sorcerer Matoriv"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:23:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
